metadata.name: incubation
metadata.description:
「孵化」”incubation”

I depicted a scene in the near future where a girl sleeping in a shelter resembling an egg awakens and tries to break out of her shell into the outside world by her own power.
The motif of the work is "incubation" and the themes of "growth" and "life" are depicted.
It is a work that I am very attached to, and was painted at a time when I wanted to seriously try my hand at painting.
